---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SocialLinks from '../components/SocialLinks.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Sifath Arora — a Redmond High School freshman passionate about dentistry, chemistry, music, and community advocacy."
>
  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="container about-hero-inner">
      <div class="about-intro">
        <img
          src="/images/sifath.jpg"
          alt="Sifath Arora"
          class="about-photo"
          width="140"
          height="140"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <p class="section-label">About</p>
        <h1>Sifath Arora</h1>
        <p class="about-tagline">
          Freshman at Redmond High · aspiring dentist · community builder
        </p>
      </div>
      <dl class="about-facts">
        <div class="fact">
          <dt>School</dt>
          <dd>Redmond High School, 9th grade</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <dt>GPA</dt>
          <dd>4.0</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <dt>Currently</dt>
          <dd>Chemistry &amp; biology coursework</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact">
          <dt>Contact</dt>
          <dd><SocialLinks variant="stacked" /></dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container about-body">
    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>What drives me</h2>
      <div class="about-columns">
        <p>
          I've always gravitated toward science — especially anything connected to health.
          Dentistry caught my attention because it's hands-on, creative, and deeply personal.
          Helping someone feel confident in their smile is a kind of care that stays with them.
        </p>
        <p>
          This year I'm taking chemistry, and it's changed how I think about the dental topics
          I write about each week. Understanding ions, pH, and chemical bonding gives me a
          deeper lens on enamel, cavities, and the science behind everyday oral health.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Beyond the classroom</h2>
      <ul class="activity-list">
        <li>
          <strong>First Chair Violin</strong>
          <span>School orchestra — eight years of performance and discipline</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Varsity Slow-Pitch Softball</strong>
          <span>Teamwork and competition at the varsity level</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Destination Imagination</strong>
          <span>8 years · 5× Global Finalist · 10th worldwide in improv</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Sikh Advocacy Day</strong>
          <span>Civic engagement with state legislators on inclusive education</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Religious School Volunteer</strong>
          <span>Weekly — teaching Punjabi, Sikh history, and core academics</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section project-spotlight">
      <div class="project-card">
        <p class="section-label">Featured project</p>
        <h2>Care Collective</h2>
        <p>
          I founded Care Collective to address a gap I kept noticing — families who want
          good oral health but can't always afford basic supplies. We organize donation drives
          for toothbrushes, toothpaste, floss, and educational materials, then distribute them
          through community partners.
        </p>
        <p>
          It's my way of connecting the science I learn with the service I believe in.
          Dentistry isn't just a career I'm exploring — it's a responsibility to the
          communities around me.
        </p>
        <a href="/research/care-collective" class="project-link">Read about the project &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Interests</h2>
      <ul class="interest-tags">
        <li>Dentistry</li>
        <li>Chemistry</li>
        <li>Biology</li>
        <li>Community Service</li>
        <li>Cultural Advocacy</li>
        <li>Music</li>
        <li>Research</li>
        <li>Public Speaking</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="container resume-block" id="resume">
    <p class="section-label">Resume</p>
    <h2>Experience &amp; achievements</h2>

    <div class="resume-grid">
      <section class="resume-section">
        <h3>Education</h3>
        <div class="resume-item">
          <strong>Redmond High School</strong>
          <span>Redmond, WA — 9th Grade · GPA 4.0</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h3>Projects</h3>
        <div class="resume-item">
          <strong>Care Collective</strong>
          <span>Founder</span>
          <p>Community initiative collecting and distributing dental care supplies to underserved families.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-item">
          <strong>Life Science &amp; Dentistry Capstone</strong>
          <span>3rd Place</span>
          <p>Research project exploring connections between life science and dentistry.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h3>Leadership &amp; Advocacy</h3>
        <div class="resume-item">
          <strong>Sikh Advocacy Day Participant</strong>
          <p>Advocated for inclusive education and Sikh representation in curriculum with state legislators.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-item">
          <strong>Education &amp; Culture Blog Creator</strong>
          <p>Weekly dental journal and writing on Sikh identity, student experiences, and cultural representation.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h3>Volunteer</h3>
        <div class="resume-item">
          <strong>Religious School Volunteer</strong>
          <span>Federal Way, WA — Weekly</span>
          <p>Teach Punjabi, Sikh history, and core academics. Organize math competitions and mentor students.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h3>Activities</h3>
        <ul class="compact-list">
          <li>Varsity Slow-Pitch Softball</li>
          <li>Orchestra — First Chair Violin</li>
          <li>Destination Imagination (5× Global Finalist)</li>
          <li>DECA — Business Law &amp; Ethics</li>
          <li>Science Olympiad — Top 3 regional &amp; state</li>
          <li>National Junior Honor Society</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h3>Achievements</h3>
        <ul class="compact-list">
          <li>10th Place Worldwide, DI Global Finals (Improv)</li>
          <li>Regional Winner, Sikh Youth Symposium</li>
          <li>3rd Place, Life Science &amp; Dentistry Capstone</li>
          <li>Winner, Research Capstone Final Contact Contest</li>
          <li>First Chair Violinist, School Orchestra</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 4.5rem) 0;
    background: var(--bg-soft);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: end;
  }

  .about-intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    border: 3px solid var(--bg-elevated);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .about-tagline {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-facts {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .fact dt {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .fact dd {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .fact dd :global(.social-links) {
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
  }

  .about-body {
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem) 0;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.65rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .about-columns p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .activity-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .activity-list li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 11rem 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.35rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .activity-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .activity-list strong {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .activity-list span {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .project-spotlight {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .project-card {
    padding: 2rem 2.25rem;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .project-card h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .project-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .project-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .interest-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .interest-tags li {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--accent-light);
    color: var(--accent-dark);
  }

  .resume-block {
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 3rem;
  }

  .resume-block > h2 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .resume-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem 3rem;
  }

  .compact-list {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .compact-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero-inner,
    .about-columns,
    .resume-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-facts {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .activity-list li {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
